name: UPL Limited
description: UPL Limited, formerly United Phosphorus Limited, is an Indian multinational company that manufactures and markets agrochemicals and specialty chemicals, and also offers pesticides.

name: Tata Chemicals
description: Tata Chemicals Limited is an Indian global company with interests in chemicals, crop protection and specialty chemistry products headquartered in Mumbai, India.

name: TATA Agrico
description: TATA Agrico has in its product range both conventional tools used for gardening include pruning & roll cut secateurs, digging trowels, weeding forks & hedge shears.

name: Corteva
description: Corteva, Inc. is a major American agricultural chemical and seed company that was the agricultural unit of DowDuPont prior to being spun off as an independent public company.

name: AllThatGrows
description: We are a company which brings to you the best, most healthful and nourishing seeds. Our experience of producing and supplying superior quality seeds spans over a decade.
